《'''星際爭霸戰：發現號'''》（{{lang-en|''Star Trek: Discovery''}}）是一部由[[布萊恩·富勒|布萊恩·富勒]]與[[艾力克斯·寇茲曼|艾力克斯·寇茲曼]]開創，於{{le|CBS通路全開|CBS All Access}}（後來更名為[[派拉蒙+|派拉蒙+]]）首播的[[美國|美國]][[科幻片|科幻]][[劇情片|劇情]][[電視劇|電視劇]]<ref name="cnet20170925">{{cite news|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/star-trek-discovery-how-to-watch-stream-release-date-time-cbs-new-netflix/|script-title=en:'Star Trek: Discovery' launches tonight! Here's how to see it|author=Amanda Kooser|date=2017-09-25|publisher=Cnet|accessdate=2017-10-16|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222184857/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/star-trek-discovery-how-to-watch-stream-release-date-time-cbs-new-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="forbes20170926">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/26/why-cbs-is-right-to-make-audiences-pay-for-star-trek-discovery/#273538cc4e94|script-title=en:CBS Is Right To Make Us Pay For 'Star Trek: Discovery'|author=Scott Mendelson|date=2017-09-29|publisher=Forbes|access-date=2017-10-16|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112020401/https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2017/09/26/why-cbs-is-right-to-make-audiences-pay-for-star-trek-discovery/#273538cc4e94|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這是《[[星艦奇航記|星際爭霸戰]]》系列自從《[[星艦前傳|星際爭霸戰：星艦前傳]]》於2005年完結以來的第一部電視劇，也是該系列的第七部。本劇是以全新角色為主，與2009年電影《[[星際爭霸戰_(電影)|星際爭霸戰]]》的[[星际旅行正典#凱文時間線|新世界觀]]毫無關聯<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/culture/content-33599.html|title=楊紫瓊化身星艦艦長？全新影集《星際爭霸戰：發現號》9月底登場|date=2017-09-11|author=Eric|work=GQ Taiwan|access-date=2017-10-08|archive-date=2017-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008184312/https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/culture/content-33599.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。故事設定於電視劇《[[星際爭霸戰|-{zh-cn:星际旅行：原初系列;zh-tw:星際爭霸戰;zh-hk:星空奇遇記}-]]》故事的十年前<ref name="FullerAug2016 /">{{cite web |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/star-trek-discovery/ |title=Star Trek: Discovery: 11 Things We Learned About The New Trek Series [TCA 2016] |last=Topel |first=Fred |work={{lang-en|/Film|/Film}} |publisher=[[Blogger|Blogger]] |location=United States |date=2016-08-11 |accessdate=2016-11-30 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6mOGFXMHk?url=http://www.slashfilm.com/star-trek-discovery/ |archivedate=2016-11-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="dexpress-858496"/>，約2256年左右，並於第三季拓展至3188年。

該劇定於2017年9月24日首播，{{le|星際爭霸戰：發現號 (第一季)|Star Trek: Discovery (season 1)|第一季}}共15集<ref name="dexpress-858496">{{cite news|url=http://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/858496/star-trek-discovery-how-many-episodes-release-date-netflix-trailer-cast|title=Star Trek: Discovery – How many episodes are there? When is the next one out on Netflix?|author=Reiss Smith|date=Sep 25, 2017|newspaper=Daily Express|accessdate=2017-11-09|archive-date=2020-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200806171426/https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/858496/star-trek-discovery-how-many-episodes-release-date-netflix-trailer-cast|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而{{le|星際爭霸戰：發現號 (第二季)|Star Trek: Discovery (season 2)|第二季}}則在2019年1月17日首播，合共14集<ref>{{Cite web|title=Anson Mount Reveals ‘Star Trek: Discovery’ Season 2 Has Been Extended To 14 Episodes|url=https://trekmovie.com/2018/12/08/anson-mount-reveals-star-trek-discovery-season-2-has-been-extended-to-14-episodes/|work=TrekMovie.com|accessdate=2019-03-17|language=en-US|first=TrekMovie com|last=Staff|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308061245/https://trekmovie.com/2018/12/08/anson-mount-reveals-star-trek-discovery-season-2-has-been-extended-to-14-episodes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年2月，CBS正式續訂{{le|星際爭霸戰：發現號 (第三季)|Star Trek: Discovery (season 3)|第三季}}<ref name="Season3Renewal">{{Cite news |last=Otterson |first=Joe |date=February 27, 2019 |title=‘Star Trek: Discovery’ Renewed for Season 3, Michelle Paradise Upped to Co-Showrunner |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |url=https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/star-trek-discovery-renewed-season-3-cbs-all-access-michelle-paradise-co-showrunner-1203150809/ |url-status=live |access-date=February 27, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227230535/https://variety.com/2019/tv/news/star-trek-discovery-renewed-season-3-cbs-all-access-michelle-paradise-co-showrunner-1203150809/ |archive-date=February 27, 2019}}</ref>，於2020年10月首播，同时也正式續訂{{le|星際爭霸戰：發現號 (第四季)|Star Trek: Discovery (season 4)|第四季}}<ref name="Season4Renewal">{{Cite web |last=Petski |first=Denise |date=October 16, 2020 |title='Star Trek: Discovery' Renewed For Season 4 By CBS All Access, Gets Production Start Date |url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/star-trek-discovery-renewed-season-4-cbs-all-access-production-start-date-1234598765/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018201723/https://deadline.com/2020/10/star-trek-discovery-renewed-season-4-cbs-all-access-production-start-date-1234598765/ |archive-date=October 18, 2020 |access-date=October 18, 2020 |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]}}</ref>，於2020年11月開拍，預計於2021年在派拉蒙+首播<ref name="STUParamountPlus">{{Cite web |last1=Vary |first1=Adam B. |date=February 24, 2021 |title=Inside the 'Star Trek' Universe of New Shows and Kids' Fare on Paramount Plus |url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/star-trek-universe-paramount-plus-prodigy-1234914526/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225051556/https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/star-trek-universe-paramount-plus-prodigy-1234914526/ |archive-date=February 25, 2021 |access-date=February 27, 2021 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]}}</ref>。

== 劇情大綱 ==
本劇故事大約在《[[星際爭霸戰|星際爭霸戰]]》事件發生的前十年開始<ref name="FullerAug2016">{{Cite web |last=Hibberd |first=James |date=August 10, 2016 |title=Star Trek: Major details revealed about new TV show |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/08/10/star-trek-tv-series |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6jfxvfmma?url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/08/10/star-trek-tv-series |archive-date=August 11, 2016 |access-date=August 11, 2016 |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |publisher=[[Time_Inc.|Time Inc.]] |location=United States |quote=''Star Trek: Discovery'' will be set in the 'Prime Universe' (so in the timeline of the original shows, not the J.J. Abrams reboot films), about a decade before Captain Kirk's five-year mission.}}</ref>，第一季將看到[[克林貢|克林貢]]家族在與[[星際聯邦|星際聯邦]]的戰爭後團結起來，這場戰爭嚴重涉及聯邦星艦[[發現號_(NCC-1031)|發現號（NCC-1031）]]的船員<ref name="KlingonsDesign" /><ref name="SDCCGalleryKlingons">{{Cite web |last=Ulster |first=Laurie |date=July 20, 2017 |title=SDCC17: See 'Star Trek: Discovery' Klingon Costumes And Props |url=http://trekmovie.com/2017/07/20/sdcc17-star-trek-discovery-klingon-costumes-and-props/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6s8RIWopQ?url=http://trekmovie.com/2017/07/20/sdcc17-star-trek-discovery-klingon-costumes-and-props/ |archive-date=July 22, 2017 |access-date=July 22, 2017 |website=TrekMovie.com}}</ref>。第二季戰爭結束後，發現號調查了七個神秘信號和一個被稱為「紅天使」的奇異人物<ref name="SpockPremiere">{{Cite web |last=Bloom |first=Mike |date=October 6, 2018 |title='Star Trek: Discovery' Debuts First-Look at Spock in Season 2 Trailer |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/star-trek-discovery-spock-revealed-season-2-trailer-1149992 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007021804/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/star-trek-discovery-spock-revealed-season-2-trailer-1149992 |archive-date=October 7, 2018 |access-date=October 7, 2018 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref>。 第三季則是發現號前往32世紀，即他們的未來900多年，為這場衝突畫下句點<ref name="KurtzmanPostS2THR">{{Cite web |last=Bloom |first=Mike |date=April 18, 2019 |title=How the 'Star Trek: Discovery' Finale Pulled Off the Franchise's Boldest Leap Yet |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/star-trek-discovery-season-2-finale-time-jump-explained-1203166 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419023639/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/star-trek-discovery-season-2-finale-time-jump-explained-1203166 |archive-date=April 19, 2019 |access-date=April 20, 2019 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref>。第四季描述在《星際爭霸戰》事件發生的900多年後，發現號的船員們面臨著一種無形的異常<ref name="Season4Renewal"/>。

